      <h3><a name="reqs">Requirements</a></h3>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="http://code.google.com/p/httplib2/">httplib2</a> 0.5.0 or newer.</li>
        <li><a href="http://code.google.com/p/simplejson/">simplejson</a> with Python older than 2.6</li>
      </ul>
